quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  70,11,"A pukhailai ran siran. Ma­pundingandingan o baradosa: A o ba niyambo khirunding ko siksa sa Alongan noto so manga Wata iyan,"
  70,12,"Go so Karoma niyan, go so Pagari niyan,"
  70,13,"Go so manga Tonganai niyan a so mithitimo iyan,"
  70,14,"Go so matatago ko Lopa, langon, oriyan niyan na sabutun sukaniyan (o Allah)."
  70,15,"Di dun noto; ka Mata-an naya! A kadug,"
  70,16,"A Phulodas ko kobal ko Olo!"
  70,17,"Puthawagun niyan so tao a tomiyalikhod go Mimbarapaling,"
  70,18,"Go miyanimo na miyamotal (sa tamok)!"
  70,19,"Mata-an! A so Manosiya na Inadun a tithiyakha-an, mala i inam,"
  70,20,"Igira-a miyasogat sukaniyan o marata na di-i Khaminan;"
  70,21,"Na igira-a miyasogat sukani­yan o mapiya na Simpunun niyan (kadi phamumugai);"
  70,22,"Inonta so manga Barasam­bayang,"
  70,23,"A so siran na so Sambayang iran na tatatapun niran,"
  70,24,"Go siran na adun a matatago ko manga tamok iran a haq a ma­pupunto (a so Zakat),"
  70,25,"A ruk o puphamanguni, a go so di phamanguni a Karurugunan,"
  70,26,"Go siran na bubunarun niran so Alongan a kapamalas,"
  70,27,"Go siran na siran na so siksa o Kadnan niran na ika-aluk iran,-"
  70,28,"Mata-an! A so Siksa o Kad­nan niran na da-a somasarig sa kalupas iyanon,-"
  70,29,"Go siran na siran na so man­ga ginawa iran na sisiyapun niran,"
  70,30,"Inonta si-i ko manga Karoma iran, o di na so miyakhapa-ar o manga tangan niran,- ka Mata-an! A siran na da-a Pa-awing iran non,-"
  70,31,"Na sa tao a mamagingar sa salakao ro-o na siran man na siran i manga malawani;"
  70,32,"Go siran na siran na so man­ga sarig kiran, a go so diyandi kiran na sisiyapun niran,"
  70,33,"Go siran na siran na so ka­ shasaksi-an niran na i Pamamayan­dug iran,"
  70,34,"Go siran na siran na so Sam­bayang iran na sisiyapun niran."
  70,35,"Siran man i khatago ko man­ga Sorga, a Khisusula-an siran."
  70,36,"Na antona-a so Miyaman­gongkir a mapapantag Ka a khila­langag."
  70,37,"Si-i sa kawanan a go sa diyo­wang a khokoliling siran?"
  70,38,"Ba mai inam o omani isa kiran a kapakasoluda-on ko Sorga a pakadarandang?"
  70,39,"Di dun noto! Mata-an! A Sukami na Inadun Ami siran pho­on ko nganin a katawan niran (a Notfa)!"